"index_reference": "5119: solomon, life of",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Solomon succeeded his father David as king and secured Israel's stability through treaties with foreign powers.</p>\n<h2>Solomon's birth</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr3:1-1Chr3:9\">1CH 3:1–3:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam12:24-2Sam12:25\">2SA 12:24–12:25</a></p>\n<h2>Solomon's accession</h2>\n<h3>Adonijah's rivalry</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs1:5\">1KI 1:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs1:11-1Kgs1:14\">1KI 1:11–1:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs1:24-1Kgs1:25\">1KI 1:24–1:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs2:13-1Kgs2:25\">1KI 2:13–2:25</a></p>\n<h3>David's approval</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs1:30\">1KI 1:30</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:23\">1CH 29:23</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs1:32-1Kgs1:35\">1KI 1:32–1:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs2:1-1Kgs2:4\">1KI 2:1–2:4</a></p>\n<h3>The coronation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs1:38-1Kgs1:40\">1KI 1:38–1:40</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:21-1Chr29:22\">1CH 29:21–29:22</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs2:12\">1KI 2:12</a></p>\n<h2>Solomon's administration of Israel</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs4:7\">1KI 4:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs4:20-1Kgs4:25\">1KI 4:20–4:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs4:27\">1KI 4:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:25-1Kgs10:27\">1KI 10:25–10:27</a></p>\n<h2>Solomon's building projects</h2>\n<h3>The temple</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr3:1\">2CH 3:1</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:1\">1KI 6:1</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs5:5-1Kgs5:6\">1KI 5:5–5:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs5:10-1Kgs5:11\">1KI 5:10–5:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:14\">1KI 6:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:37-1Kgs6:38\">1KI 6:37–6:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:63\">1KI 8:63</a></p>\n<h3>The palace</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:1-1Kgs7:3\">1KI 7:1–7:3</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Other building projects</h2>\n<p><em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs9:15-1Kgs9:19\">1KI 9:15–9:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr9:20\">2CH 9:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl2:6\">ECC 2:6</a> <em>Solomon's Pools</em><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:7-1Kgs7:8\">1KI 7:7–7:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:23\">JHN 10:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:11\">ACT 3:11</a></p>\n<h2>Solomon's many wives</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs11:1-1Kgs11:5\">1KI 11:1–11:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs3:1\">1KI 3:1</a></p>\n<h2>Solomon's death</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs11:42-1Kgs11:43\">1KI 11:42–11:43</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr9:30-2Chr9:31\">2CH 9:30–9:31</a></p>",
